# Wellfit QA — CNP PaymentTokens (STAGE)

## Important

`TokenVault.dbo.PaymentTokens.ProcessorToken` values (e.g. `WPAC4T*`) often return **Token was not found** on legacy `process-card`.

For 9.6 CNP regression: run collection folder **00b. Tokenize cards** (`POST …/credit-card/tokenize-card`) first — scripts save live tokens into `tokenVisa` / `tokenAmex` / `tokenDiscover` / `tokenMc`.

## Where (inventory / brand labels only)

- **DB:** `TokenVault` — table `dbo.PaymentTokens` (brand inventory SQL still useful)
- **Live charge tokens:** create via **tokenize-card** on STAGE Payments API

## Canonical inventory query

`regression/9.6/scripts/cnp-payment-tokens-by-brand-STAGE.sql` — brand counts / labels only; prefer tokenize-card for runnable tokens.

## Postman env mapping (9.6 CNP)

| Env key | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `tokenVisa` | CardBrand VISA / VI |
| `tokenAmex` | AMEX / AX |
| `tokenDiscover` | Discover / DI / DS |
| `tokenMc` | MasterCard / MC |
| `tokenVisaZipSensitive` | Optional — ZIP/CVV negatives only |

